# Next.js + shadcn/ui Rules

## Server vs Client

- Default to Server Components. Add `"use client"` only for hooks/events/browser APIs.
- Heavy client components (Monaco, R3F) must be `dynamic()` imported with `ssr: false`.

## shadcn/ui

- Install via `npx shadcn@latest add <name>`.
- Import from `@/components/ui/`.
- Use `variant` and `size` props consistently.
- Colors via CSS variables (`bg-background`, `text-foreground`).

## Styling

- Tailwind utilities only. No inline `style={}` unless dynamic.
- Mobile-first responsive: `sm:`, `md:`, `lg:`.
- Spacing: use default Tailwind scale.

## File Conventions

- Pages: `app/**/page.tsx`, Layouts: `app/**/layout.tsx`
- Components: PascalCase in `components/` directory
- Utilities: `lib/` directory
